cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on deep neural networks and their robustness against input perturbations, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments are conducted on image classification tasks, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of adversarial examples, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for improving the robustness of neural networks, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
